{"id":261,"parent_id":245,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":261,"title":"1 Samuel 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord chooses David of Bethlehem as king—He is anointed by Samuel—Saul chooses David as his companion and armor bearer."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.1","order":"02.10.016.21618"},["b","1"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Samuel, How long wilt thou mourn for Saul, seeing I have rejected him from reigning over Israel? fill thine horn with oil, and go, I will send thee to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Jesse"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Beth-lehemite"],": for I have provided me a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"king"],"among his sons."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.2","order":"02.10.016.21619"},["b","2"],"And Samuel said, How can I go? if Saul hear",["i","it,"],"he will kill me. And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said, Take an heifer with thee, and say, I am come to sacrifice to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.3","order":"02.10.016.21620"},["b","3"],"And call Jesse to the sacrifice, and I will shew thee what thou shalt do: and thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"anoint"],"unto me",["i","him"],"whom I name unto thee."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.4","order":"02.10.016.21621"},["b","4"],"And Samuel did that which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake, and came to Beth-lehem. And the elders of the town trembled at his coming, and said, Comest thou peaceably?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.5","order":"02.10.016.21622"},["b","5"],"And he said, Peaceably: I am come to sacrifice unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],":",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"sanctify"],"yourselves, and come with me to the sacrifice. And he sanctified Jesse and his sons, and called them to the sacrifice."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.6","order":"02.10.016.21623"},["b","6"],"¶And it came to pass, when they were come, that he looked on",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Eliab"],", and said, Surely the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s anointed",["i","is"],"before him."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7","order":"02.10.016.21624"},["b","7"],"But the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto Samuel, Look not on his countenance, or on the height of his stature; because I have refused him: for",["i","the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"seeth"]],"not as",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"man"],"seeth; for man looketh on the outward",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"appearance"],", but the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"Lord"]],"looketh on the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_7e"},"heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.8","order":"02.10.016.21625"},["b","8"],"Then Jesse called Abinadab, and made him pass before Samuel. And he said, Neither hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"chosen this."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.9","order":"02.10.016.21626"},["b","9"],"Then Jesse made Shammah to pass by. And he said, Neither hath the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"chosen this."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.10","order":"02.10.016.21627"},["b","10"],"Again, Jesse made seven of his sons to pass before Samuel. And Samuel said unto Jesse, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath not chosen these."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.11","order":"02.10.016.21628"},["b","11"],"And Samuel said unto Jesse, Are here all",["i","thy"],"children? And he said, There remaineth yet the youngest, and, behold, he keepeth the sheep. And Samuel said unto Jesse, Send and fetch him: for we will not sit down till he come hither."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.12","order":"02.10.016.21629"},["b","12"],"And he sent, and brought him in. Now he",["i","was"],"ruddy,",["i","and"],"withal of a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"beautiful"],"countenance, and goodly to look to. And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said, Arise, anoint him: for this",["i","is"],"he."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.13","order":"02.10.016.21630"},["b","13"],"Then Samuel took the horn of oil, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"anointed"],"him in the midst of his brethren: and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"Spirit"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came upon",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"David"],"from that day forward. So Samuel rose up, and went to Ramah."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.14","order":"02.10.016.21631"},["b","14"],"¶But the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Spirit"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"departed"],"from Saul, and an evil spirit",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"from the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"]],"troubled him."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.15","order":"02.10.016.21632"},["b","15"],"And Saul’s servants said unto him, Behold now, an evil spirit",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"from God"],"troubleth thee."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.16","order":"02.10.016.21633"},["b","16"],"Let our lord now command thy servants,",["i","which are"],"before thee, to seek out a man,",["i","who is"],"a cunning player on an harp: and it shall come to pass, when the evil spirit",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"from God"],"is upon thee, that he shall play with his hand, and thou shalt be well."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.17","order":"02.10.016.21634"},["b","17"],"And Saul said unto his servants, Provide me now a man that can play well, and bring",["i","him"],"to me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.18","order":"02.10.016.21635"},["b","18"],"Then answered one of the servants, and said, Behold, I have seen a son of Jesse the Beth-lehemite,",["i","that is"],"cunning in playing, and a mighty valiant man, and a man of war, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"prudent"],"in matters, and a comely person, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"with him."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.19","order":"02.10.016.21636"},["b","19"],"¶Wherefore Saul sent messengers unto Jesse, and said, Send me David thy son, which",["i","is"],"with the sheep."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.20","order":"02.10.016.21637"},["b","20"],"And Jesse took an ass",["i","laden"],"with bread, and a bottle of wine, and a kid, and sent",["i","them"],"by David his son unto Saul."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.21","order":"02.10.016.21638"},["b","21"],"And David came to Saul, and stood before him: and he loved him greatly; and he became his armourbearer."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.22","order":"02.10.016.21639"},["b","22"],"And Saul sent to Jesse, saying, Let David, I pray thee, stand before me; for he hath found favour in my sight."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.23","order":"02.10.016.21640"},["b","23"],"And it came to pass, when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},["i","evil"],"spirit"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"from God"],"was upon Saul, that David took an harp, and played with his hand: so Saul was refreshed, and was well, and the evil spirit departed from him."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.1a","order":"02.10.016.21641"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-davidic-descent-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Davidic Descent of"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.1b","order":"02.10.016.21643"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/5.2"},"Micah 5:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/2.4"},"Luke 2:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/7.42.41-44"},"John 7:42 (41–44)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.1c","order":"02.10.016.21645"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.16"},"1 Kgs. 8:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/11.3"},"1 Chr. 11:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/28.4"},"28:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.3a","order":"02.10.016.21647"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.5a","order":"02.10.016.21649"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/19.10"},"Ex. 19:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.6a","order":"02.10.016.21651"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/17.13"},"1 Sam. 17:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/2.13"},"1 Chr. 2:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/11.18"},"2 Chr. 11:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7a","order":"02.10.016.21653"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/10.4"},"Job 10:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7b","order":"02.10.016.21655"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/55.8.8-9"},"Isa. 55:8 (8–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7c","order":"02.10.016.21657"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/10.7"},"2 Cor. 10:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/discernment-spiritual"},"TG Discernment, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7d","order":"02.10.016.21659"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"TG God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.7e","order":"02.10.016.21661"},["b","7e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heart"},"TG Heart"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.12a","order":"02.10.016.21663"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/beauty"},"TG Beauty"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.13a","order":"02.10.016.21665"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/89.20"},"Ps. 89:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.13b","order":"02.10.016.21667"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gift-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gift of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.13c","order":"02.10.016.21669"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/17.12"},"1 Sam. 17:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/2.15"},"1 Chr. 2:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/78.70"},"Ps. 78:70"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.14a","order":"02.10.016.21671"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-loss-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Loss of"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.14b","order":"02.10.016.21673"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/28.15.15-16"},"1 Sam. 28:15 (15–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.12"},"Hosea 9:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.14c","order":"02.10.016.21675"},["b","14c"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Sam. 16:14 …",["i","which was not of"],"the Lord …"],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.15a","order":"02.10.016.21677"},["b","15a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Sam. 16:15 …",["i","which is not of"],"God …"],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.16a","order":"02.10.016.21679"},["b","16a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Sam. 16:16 …",["i","which is not of"],"God …"],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.18a","order":"02.10.016.21681"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prudence"},"TG Prudence"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.23a","order":"02.10.016.21683"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"},"TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/16.23b","order":"02.10.016.21685"},["b","23b"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Sam. 16:23 …",["i","which was not of"],"God …"]]}
